## Dependencies
- Requires: Member Management (member data)
- Requires: Staff Management (trainer accounts)
- Requires: Authentication System (trainer login)
- Connected to: Member check-in system

## Access Control
- **Owner**: Can assign members to trainers
- **Receptionist**: No access to trainer assignments
- **Trainer**: View assigned members only (cannot modify)

## Business Rules
- Only active trainers can have member assignments
- Members can be assigned to one trainer at a time
- Trainers can view only their assigned members
- Assignments persist even if member becomes inactive
- Terminated trainers lose access to members

## Trainer Capabilities

### What Trainers CAN Do:
- View their assigned members
- See member contact information
- Check member membership status
- View member join dates

### What Trainers CANNOT Do:
- Register new members
- Modify member information
- Process payments
- Access other trainers' members
- Manage staff or equipment

## Integration Points

### With Member Management
- Members assigned to trainers
- Trainer ID stored in member record
- Assignment displayed in member details

### With Staff Management
- Trainers are staff with role "Trainer"
- Trainer salary management
- Active/Inactive status affects assignments

### With Authentication
- Trainer-specific login flow
- Role-based access control
- Session management for trainers

## Future Enhancements
